This project contains source code and sample data for the program
SVDClus, as described in the paper:
'An investigation of the use of spectral clustering for the analysis
of molecular data'

Sonny Gan, David A Cosgrove, Eleanor J Gardiner and Valerie J Gillet.

Submitted to the Journal of Chemical Information and Modelling,
currently under revision.

Please see the src directory for more details. It is licensed under
the "New BSD" license, please see src/license.txt (or file LICENSE
in this directory, a symbolic link to it) for details. File src/README
contains information on building the program on a linux platform.
